{
  "texts": [
    "All models were trained for 500 iterations for each task, using Adam with a learning rate of 0.01 for the DINER models and 0.001 for the other models.",
    "For the P.E.",
    "ReLU models, we used a positional encoding level L = 10.",
    "The SIREN and FINER models used ω 0 = 15 and ω 0 = 5, respectively.",
    "The DINER models used latent space dimensionality L = 1.We considered two different continual learning scenarios (Fig. 2)."
  ]
}